Task 1: Capture and Analyze Cookies with Burp Suite
Step 1: Start Services and Configure Proxy
Start DVWA services:

sudo systemctl start apache2 mysql
firefox http://localhost/dvwa &
Login to DVWA (admin/password), then start Burp Suite:

burpsuite &
Configure Firefox proxy:

Preferences > Network Settings > Manual proxy
HTTP Proxy: 127.0.0.1, Port: 8080
Check "Use this proxy for all protocols"
Step 2: Intercept and Examine Session Cookies
In Burp Suite:

Navigate to Proxy > Intercept tab
Ensure "Intercept is on"
In Firefox, navigate to any DVWA page
In Burp Suite, examine the intercepted request
Look for:

Cookie: header in requests
Set-Cookie: header in responses
Cookie attributes: HttpOnly, Secure, SameSite, Path, Domain
Forward the request and disable intercept. Go to Proxy > HTTP history to review all cookie exchanges.

