Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Burp Suite not intercepting traffic

Solution: Verify Firefox proxy settings point to 127.0.0.1:8080
Check that Burp Suite proxy listener is active on port 8080
Issue: Python script cannot connect to DVWA

Solution: Ensure Apache and MySQL services are running
Verify DVWA is accessible at http://localhost/dvwa/
Check for firewall blocking local connections
Issue: No session tokens collected

Solution: Verify you're logged into DVWA before collecting tokens
Check that the target URL is correct
Ensure cookies are enabled in browser
Issue: Import errors in Python scripts

Solution: Install required libraries: pip3 install requests --user
Verify Python 3.x is being used: python3 --version
